OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry start
OL,6,Fwith some clear spells, but cloud will
OL,7,Fthicken overnight. A few outbreaks of
OL,8,Frain may develop by early Saturday,
OL,9,Fwith a low risk of heavy bursts and
OL,10,Fthunder. Winds will remain generally
OL,11,Flight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FAny cloud and rain should
OL,14,Fquickly clear to give a bright, sunny
OL,15,Fand warm day. Staying a little cooler
OL,16,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
